WEBVTT

00:01.300 --> 00:02.934
Hi... <i>ya!</i>

00:03.001 --> 00:04.135
Let me guess.

00:04.203 --> 00:06.737
They're doing <i>A Chorus Line</i>
and you're Cassie?

00:06.805 --> 00:08.406
I, Salem, have taken up Tae Bo.

00:08.474 --> 00:12.076
Instead of conquering the world,
I'm just going to kick butt.

00:12.144 --> 00:13.044
You can't learn Tae Bo.

00:13.112 --> 00:14.779
You have no body weight
or leg extension,

00:14.847 --> 00:16.248
not to mention will or courage.

00:16.315 --> 00:17.248
Perfect.

00:17.316 --> 00:19.717
I will use that
as my daily affirmation.

00:19.785 --> 00:21.419
I think you're going
to need some help.

00:24.157 --> 00:25.123
SALEM:
Billy Blanks!

00:25.191 --> 00:26.257
I am your clay.

00:26.325 --> 00:27.425
Mold me.

00:30.495 --> 00:31.929
Now, that doesn't look so hard.

00:33.799 --> 00:34.699
(Salem yells)

00:34.766 --> 00:37.201
Salem, are you okay?

00:37.269 --> 00:38.269
(panting)

00:38.337 --> 00:39.271
(spitting)

00:39.338 --> 00:41.339
I love this sport!

00:41.407 --> 00:43.108
(sighing)

00:45.878 --> 00:47.712
¶ ¶

